reviewText: Of the Peach dvds I've seen, this is the best. If you are looking for hardcore porn, this isn't it, and there are billions of other venues out there for that. It is a pretty girl dvd. I like this one the best for several reason. First, all but one of the ladies are quite stunning, esp Alyssa Lovelace and my favorite, Nicole Leshell. Second, the multi angle feature allows for full body views, as well as close up views. I love this feature, as I think a beautiful woman's face is important in the erotic and sensual recipe. Also, I use this dvd for drawing, making these gorgeous ladies my own person models. The other Peach dvds I have lack the multi-angle feature, so that you only get one view at a time, be it close up or full body, and that limits my enjoyment and utility of the images. Again, it's a pretty girl dvd, not a gynocological dvd, it's not advertised as such, so don't complain if it's not all pink.
